A generic tradeoff plot based on two functions of class PM

A generic tradeoff plot based on two functions of class PM

tradeoff(MSE, PMs)

Arguments

MSE
an object of class MSE
PMs
a list of named functions of class PM

Value

a trade-off figure classy

Examples

loadABT()
#> ABT-MSE objects loaded
tradeoff(MSE_example,list(POF=POF,Y10=Y10))
